column5: Salmon was from last night. 2 for 2. Bass was on monday. The blurry image was the largest bass and a personal best, and caught around July, close to 5 lber.   http://i223.photobucket.com/albums/dd294/b...rontosept29.jpg  http://i223.photobucket.com/albums/dd294/b...bum/3lbbass.jpg  http://i223.photobucket.com/albums/dd294/b...r_album/hog.jpg  All fish released as always
